# todo
create godlike script (or find app) that automates the environment described
below

# windows ui
use aquasnap
dock taskbar to left side

# windows apps notes
use chocolatey to install apps
use notepad++ in post-it mode (F12)
use regedit as much as possible to customise environment, don't use menus
use WSL (available Win10)
use git bash

## optional
use high-contrast mode (optional!)
use mouse keys (keypad moves mouse)

# chrome
pin frequently used tabs
consider using `More tools -> Add to desktop` if you use a webpage frequently
